hadiths[39]{hadithnumber,text}:
667,"Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur namaz key oqaat key mutalliq sawal kiya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye do din hamarey sath namazein padho. to jab suraj dhalaa aap ney Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhoney Azan kahi, phir hukm diya to unhoney Zohar ki iqaamat kahi (aur namaz ada ki gaee), phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya to unhoney Asr ki iqaamat kahi, jabke suraj buland, safed aur roshan tha. phir hukm diya to unhoney maghrib ki iqaamat kahi jab suraj ghurub huwa, phir jab shafaq ghurub ho gaee to unhen hukm diya aur unhoney Isha ki iqaamat kahi, phir jab subah saadiq tulu hui to unhen hukm diya aur unhoney Fajr ki iqaamat kahi. (is tarah paanchon namazein awwal waqt mein ada farmaeen.) jab doosra din huwa to unhen hukm diya aur unhoney thandi kar key Zohar ki Azan di aur khub hi thandi ki, phir Asr ki namaz padhi jabke suraj buland tha, lekin kal ki nisbat takheer (deri) farmaai, phir shafaq ghurub honey sey pehley maghrib ki namaz padhi aur tihai raat guzarney key baad Isha ki namaz ada farmaai, phir Fajr ki namaz khub roshan kar key padhi, phir farmaya : namaz key oqaat (waqt) poochhney wala kahan hai? usney kaha , Allah key Rasool ! wo main hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo oqaat tum ney dekhey hain, tumhari namazon key oqaat (waqt) in key darmiyan hain."
668,"Imam ibne Shahab Zohri Rahimahullah sey riwayat hai ke jin dino Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez Rahimahullah Madina key governer they, (eik din) wo (Zohri) unkey gaddey par bethey they, unkey sath Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber Rahimahullah bhi they. Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez Rahimahullah ney Asr ki namaz mein takheer kar di to Urwa ney un sey kaha : suno ! Jibril (Alaihissalam) nazil huye aur unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Imam bin kar namazein padhaein (is tarah namaz key oqaat (waqt) ka ta'yun ""wahi"" ki roshni mein huwa, isliye namaz mein der karna durust nahin). umr bin Abdul-Azeez ney farmaya : Urwa ! ghor to karo, tum kya keh rahey ho? Urwa ney kaha : mainey Bashir bin Abu-Masood ko ye kehtey suna ke mainey Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye farmatey suna ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey aap ka ye irshad suna : Jibril (Alaihissalam) nazil huye, unhoney meri imaamat ki, to mainey unkey sath (un ki iqtida (pairvi) mein) namaz padhi, phir unkey sath namaz padhi , phir unkey sath namaz padhi , phir unkey sath namaz padhi , phir unkey sath namaz padhi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ungliyon sey gin kar paanch namazon ka zikr kiya."
669,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : momin khawatin Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Fajr ki namaz (baa jamaat) ada kiya karti thin, uskey baad wo gharon ko wapis jatin to unhen koi na pehchan sakta, yani andherey ki wajeh sey pehchani nahin jati thin."
670,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aayaat kareema : (وَقُرْآنَ الْفَجْرِ إِنَّ قُرْآنَ الْفَجْرِ كَانَ مَشْهُودًا)  ""aur Fajr ki tilawat, yaqinan Fajr ki namaz mein . . padhi. farishtey . . padhi. hazir hotey hain.''  ki wazahat kartey huye farmaya : is mein raat aur din key farishtey hazir hotey hain."
671,"Hazrat Mughees bin Sumayyi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Fajr ki namaz andherey mein ada ki, jab unhoney salam pheraa to mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar kaha : ye kya namaz hai? (itni sawerey namaz padha di?) unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath aur abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key sath yehi namaz (isi waqt) padhtey they. phir jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko zakhmi kiya gaya (un par qaatilaana hamla kiya gaya) to Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) roshni honey par namaz padhaaney lagey."
672,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : subah ko roshan karo, is mein ziyada sawab hai. ya farmaya : is sey tumhen ziyada sawab milega ."
673,Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki namaz us waqt ada kartey they jab suraj dhal jata tha.
674,"Hazrat Abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dophare ki namaz , jisey tum log Zohar kehtey ho, us waqt ada kartey they jab suraj dhal jata."
675,"Hazrat Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey zamin ki tapish ki shikayat ki, to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamari shikayat door na farmaai. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key shagrid) Qataan ney kaha : hamen Abu Hatim ney Ansari sey , unhoney Hazrat Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi tarah riwayat bayan ki."
676,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey zamin ki tapish ki shikayat ki, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamari shikayat door na farmaai."
677,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab garmi shadeed ho to namaz thandi kar lo kyonkey garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki bhap sey hai."
678,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab garmi shadeed ho to Zohar ki namaz thandi kar lo kyonkey garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki bhap sey hai."
679,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Zohar ko thanda karo kyonkey garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki bhap sey hai."
680,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Zohar ki namaz dophare key waqt (zawal sey fauran baad) padha kartey they, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen farmaya : namaz thandi kar lo kyonkey garmi ki shiddat jahannam ki bhap sey hai."
681,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Zohar ko thanda kar lo."
682,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Asr ki namaz ada farmatey they jabke suraj buland aur roshan hota tha. (uskey baad) agar koi shakhs Madina ki nawaahi (aas-paas) bastiyon mein jata, to wahan pahunchney tak suraj abhi buland hota tha."
683,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Asr ki namaz ada farmaai aur abhi merey sehan mein dhoop mojud thi, abhi saya (deewar par) na chadha tha."
684,"Hazrat Ali bin Abu-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghazwaae-khandaq key moqey par irshad farmaya : jis tarah un logon ney hamein Asr ki namaz sey rok diya, Allah (iski saza key tor par) unkey gharon aur qabron ko aag sey bhar dey."
685,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jiski Asr ki namaz faut ho gaee goya uskey ehale-o-ayaal aur maal aur dolat (sab kuchh) tabah aur barbad ho gaey."
686,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mushrekin ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Asr ki namaz na padhney di, yahan tak key suraj ghurub ho gaya, tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : unhoney hamein darmiyani namaz sey rok diya, Allah un ki qabron aur gharon ko aag sey bhar dey."
687,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ehad Mubarak mein hum log maghrib ki namaz padh kar aisey waqt mein farigh ho jatey they ke aadmi apna teer girney ki jagah dekh sakta tha. Abu Yahya Za'fraani ney Ibrahim-bin-Musa key wastey sey mazkura hadees ki tarah bayan kiya."
688,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz maghrib us waqt ada kartey they, jab suraj ot mein chhup jata."
689,"Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat us waqt tak deene-fitrat (deen Islam) par qaaim rahegi, jab tak maghrib mein itni takheer na karey ke sitarey khub nikal aaeyn. Imam Abu-Adbullah Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey Muhammad bin Yahya sey suna , wo kehtey they ke log Baghdaad mein is hadees key barey mein muztarib (pareshaan) huye to main aur Abu-Bakar Al Aein Awam bin Ibaad bin Awam key paas gaey to wo apney baap ki asal (kitab) hamarey paas laye, to is mein ye hadees mojud thi."
690,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye baat na hoti ke meri ummat par mashaqqat hogi, to main unhen Isha ki namaz takheer sey padhney ka hukm deta."
691,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar mujhey apni ummat par mashaqqat ka khof na hota to main Isha ki namaz ko tihai raat ya nisf (aadhi) raat tak muakhkhar (der) karta."
692,"Hazrat Humeed (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey daryaft kiya gaya, kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney angoothi banwaai thi? unhoney farmaya : haan, eik raat aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Isha ki namaz ko aadhi raat key qarib tak muakhkhar (deri) kiya. jab namaz padh chukey to Chehra Mubarak hamari taraf kar key farmaya : logon ney namaz padh li aur so gaey aur tum jab tak namaz key intizar mein rahogey (sawab key aetbar sey) namaz hi mein (shumar) hogey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : (mujhey ab bhi wo manzar yad hai) goya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki angoothi ki chamak meri nazron key samney hai."
693,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen maghrib ki namaz padhaai , phir (Isha ki namaz key liye) bahar tashrif na laye yahan tak ke aadhi raat guzar gaee , phir aap bahar tashrif laye aur unhen namaz padhaai. phir farmaya : logon ney namaz padh li aur so gaey aur tum jab tak namaz ka intizar kartey rahey , namaz hi mein rahey. agar kamzor aur bimar afrad na hotey to mujhey yehi pasand tha ke is namaz ko aadhi raat tak muakhkhar (der) karun."
694,"Hazrat Barida Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik jang mein hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they to aap ney farmaya : badal waley din namaz jaldi padh liya karo kyonkey jiski Asr ki namaz chhoot gaee, uskey amal zaya ho gaey."
695,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya gaya ke agar koi aadmi namaz padhna bhool jaey ya soyaa reh jaey (to kya kerey)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab yad aaye , usi waqt namaz padh ley."
696,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs koi namaz padhna bhool jaey to usey chahiye ke jab usey yad aaye , padh ley."
697,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwaae-khaiber sey wapis aaye to eik raat safar jari rakha , jab neend aaney lagi to raat key aakhiri hissey mein aaram key liye thehrey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : aaj raat hamarey liye (waqt ka) khayal rakhna. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) namaz padhtey rahey jab tak un ki qismat mein hui. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Sahaba kiram so gaey. jab Fajr ka waqt qarib huwa , Bilal Fajr (key tulu honey ki simt, yani mashriq) ki taraf munh kar key apni sawari sey tek laga kar beth gaey. (taake junhi Fajr tulu ho, Azan keh den) wo sawari sey tek lagaey bethey they ke unhen neend aa gaee. na Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bedaar huye, na koi aur Sahaba bedaar huwa, yahan tak key unhen dhoop (ki garmi) mehsus hui, sab sey pehley Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aankh khuli. to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghabra gaey. farmaya : aey Bilal ! Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey maa baap aap par qurban , jis zaat ney aap ko (bedaari sey) rok liya, usi ney mujhey bhi rok liya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koochh karo. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney apni sawaariyon ko thodi door chalaya. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (qafla rok kar) wuzu kiya, aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhoney namaz ki iqaamat kahi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Fajr ki namaz padhaai. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz mukammal kar li to farmaya : jis shakhs ko namaz ki adaegi yad na rahey, usey chahiye ke jab yad aaye namaz padh ley kyonkey Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : ( وَاَقِمِ الصَّلٰوةَ لِذکْري )''aur namaz qaaim karo meri yad key liye."" Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) is aayat ko is tarah padhtey they (وَأَقِمِ الصَّلٰوةَ لِلذِّكْرٰي)''aur namaz qaaim karo, yad key waqt."
698,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney neend main apni taqseer (kamiyon) ka zikr kiya, yani ye taqseer (kami) ke wo suraj nikalney tak soey rahey. to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sotey huye (takheer ho janey mein) koi kotahi nahin, taqseer (kamiyan) (gunah) to jaagtey huye (takheer kar deney mein) hoti hai. jab koi shakhs namaz padhna bhool jaey ya soyaa reh jaey to jab usey yad aaye (ya jab bedaar ho) usi waqt namaz padh ley aur agley din uskey waqt par ada kerey. (Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) key shagrid) Hazrat Abdullah bin Ribah ney kaha : main ye hadees bayan kar raha tha ke Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi sun liya , unhoney farmaya : ladkey ! tawajjoh sey hadees bayan karo, is hadees (key irshad farmaai janey) key moqey par main bhi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha. (mainey hadees bayan ki to) unhoney hadees mein kisi ghalati ki nishan dahi nahin ki."
699,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey suraj ghurub honey sey pehley Asr ki eik rakat mil gaee, usey Asr ki namaz mil gaee aur jisey suraj tulu honey sey pehley Fajr ki eik rakat mil gaee, usey Fajr ki namaz mil gaee."
700,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney suraj tulu honey sey pehley Fajr ki eik rakat paa li , usney Fajr ki namaz paa li. aur jisney suraj ghurub honey sey pehley Asr ki eik rakat paa li , usney Asr ki namaz paa li. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : hamein Jameel bin Hasan ney Abdul-A'alaa sey , unhoney Maamar sey , unhoney Abu Salma sey, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Hurera sey bayan kiya ke be-shak Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir sabiqa riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
701,"Hazrat Abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Isha ki namaz ko der sey padhna pasand kartey they, aur is sey pehley sona aur uskey baad baaten karna napasand farmatey they."
702,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Isha ki namaz sey pehley sotey nahin they, aur Isha key baad baaten nahin kartey they."
703,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen Isha key baad baaten karney sey sakhti sey mana kiya hai."
704,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap farma rahey they : Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) tumhari namaz key naam main tum par ghalib na aa jaeyn, ye Isha hai, wo log oontniyon (ka doodh andherey key waqt dohney)  ki wajeh sey usey utma (andherey ki namaz) kehtey hain."
705,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) tumhari namaz key barey main tum par ghalib na aa jaeyn. Ibne Hurmala ney apni riwayat mein in alfaz ka izafa kiya hai : ye Isha hai, wo andhera honey par doodh dohney ki wajeh sey is (namaz) ko bhi atma (andherey ki namaz) kehtey hain."
